How to calculate the position sizing (FX lots)

  myfxbook.com/en/forex-calculators/position-size

Say we have $1000 in our account and we accept a 2% loss.

  1. Max loss: $20

  2. Entry price: $1.34

  3. Stop loss price: $1.33

  4. Position size: ?

Formula:

size   = maxLoss / (entry - stop)  / 100,000 * entry

0.0268 =   20    / ( 1.34 - 1.33 ) / 100000  * 1.34
